{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"602056b2e9","title":"对总后关于赴朝调查野战救护等工作的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"8f0f0d9c8b","index":0,"year":1952,"month":7,"day":30,"articleId":"602056b2e9"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji32","name":"毛泽东全集第32卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/32-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji32":{"comments":[{"id":"337bcc2a75","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"德怀，即彭德怀，当时任人民革命军事委员会副主席。"},{"id":"e6adec856a","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指人民革命军事委员会总后勤部1952年7月28日关于赴朝鲜调查野战救护、卫生防疫和反细菌战等项工作情况的报告。报告概述了志愿军入朝以后后勤部门在抢救、治疗、收转伤病员工作方面敢得的成绩和存在的问题，提出了以下解决问题的建议：1.连队增加卫生员人数：2.军、师、团均建立防疫组织：3.医院、医疗队装备救护车辆：4.扩大志愿军卫生部的编制：5.师以下各级卫生机关直接归同级军政首长领导；6.师休养所编制应与军的医疗所（队）相等；7.派毒气专家及化学部队到前方担任防治工作。"}],"contents":[{"id":"7894e9fd97","type":"title","text":"对总后关于赴朝调香野战救护等工作的报告的批语","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9"},{"id":"337bcc2a75","type":"paragraph","text":"德怀同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9"},{"id":"e6adec856a","type":"paragraph","text":"这个报告很好。其末条七项建议是否可行，请你和有关方面同志商处。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9"},{"id":"7dabd1e1e8","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9"},{"id":"dc663608ea","type":"paragraph","text":"七月册日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9"}],"page":{"id":"373f6625bd","publicationId":"maoquanji32","articleId":"602056b2e9","start":178,"end":178}}}},"__N_SSG":true}